  <brief_title>Changes in Myocardial Perfusion During Chronic Multi Site Biventricular Versus Right Ventricular Apex Pacing in Patients With Normal Left Ventricular Function Undergoing His Bundle Ablation for Drug-refractory Atrial Fibrillation</brief_title>
  <acronym>SOS</acronym>
  <official_title>Changes in Myocardial Perfusion During Chronic Multi Site Biventricular Versus Right Ventricular Apex Pacing in Patients With Normal Left Ventricular Function Undergoing His Bundle Ablation for Drug-refractory Atrial Fibrillation</official_title>
