  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine whether Biventricular pacing in patients undergoing HIS bundle ablation for
      atrial fibrilation has beneficial effects on myocardial perfusion and left ventricularr
      ejection fraction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
